<div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 well">
    <h1 class="text-center">ABOUT</h1>
    <hr>
    <h3>General Overview</h3>
    <div class="well">
      <p>
        This web application functions as a social connector and its primary purpose is to facilitate the connection of users who have some certain needs with other users who can fulfil those needs. Hence, users can search for, connect with, and make their requests to other users who may not be within close geographic proximity. 
      </p>
    </div>
    
    
    <h3>Technical Overview</h3>
    <div class="well">
      <ul>
        <li>Ruby 2.3.1</li>
        <li>PostgreSQL 9.3</li>
        <li>jQuery</li>
        <li>BootStrap CSS</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    
    <h3>Development Gems</h3>
    <div class="well">
      <h4>Below is a list of the gems and their use(s) in building the social application:</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Rails 4.2.5</strong> - to scaffold the application structure.</li>
        <li><strong>Devise</strong> - for user authentication, security and session management.</li>
        <li><strong>CarrierWave</strong> - to upload files from Ruby applications.</li>
        <li><strong>acts_as_votable</strong> - to implement liking feature.</li>
        <li><strong>acts_as_commentable</strong> - to implement commenting feature.</li>
        <li><strong>acts_as_follower</strong> - to create relationships between users.</li>
        <li><strong>public_activity</strong>y - to implement news feed feature.</li>
        <li><strong>will_paginate</strong> - to paginate the list of records.</li>
        <li><strong>has_friendship</strong> - to create relationships between users as friends</li>
      </ul>
      <br>
      
      <h4>JS components</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>jQuery Plugin - Date and Time Picker</li>
        <li>Ajax - to submit the forms</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>